sentences: He was born on 31 July 1967 in Kraków, Poland.
At age seventeen he won First Prize (Grand Prix) at The Student Song Festival in Kraków in 1984.
He went on to join the Piwnica pod Baranami Cabaret, composing such hits as "Znów wędrujemy", and released his first album, Naprawdę nie dzieje się nic ("Really, nothing is happening") in 1991.
Influenced by such artists as Marek Grechuta and Jan Kanty Pawluśkiewicz, his music style falls within the broad genre of sung poetry.
